Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Welcome to your dream townhome retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.87,0:00:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Step inside to a warm, inviting atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.74,0:00:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The spacious layout is perfect for modern living.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.61,0:00:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Imagine gathering in the generous living area.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Natural light floods through large windows here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Let&apos;s explore the heart of the home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The bright kitchen is truly a chef&apos;s delight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Picture yourself enjoying coffee in the breakfast nook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Marble countertops add elegance to your culinary adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Just off the kitchen, the private balcony awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Perfect for evening relaxation or morning sunshine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Now, let’s discover your versatile flex room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}This space adapts to your lifestyle beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Need a home office or guest area? It’s perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}With direct backyard access, the options are endless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}A fully fenced yard invites outdoor fun and gatherings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Children and pets will love this safe haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}As we move upstairs, let’s see the bedrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Each generously sized bedroom offers comfort and tranquility.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The bathrooms are thoughtfully designed for convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.44,0:00:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}And don’t forget about the private garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Parking is a breeze with your own driveway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}This townhome truly blends style and functionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Thank you for joining me on this tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}I can’t wait for you to call it home.
